metadata.name: Singularity
metadata.description:
Singularity: The concept of a point in time when artificial intelligence (AI) surpasses human capabilities or when it causes major changes in human life.

Epiphyllum oxypetalum: The beauty under the moon blooms for only one day, and it blooms quietly and unnoticed at night. In the language of flowers, "fleeting beauty," "hidden passion," and "I just want to see you once."
